list.item:
Immediate recognition of the right of the peoples of the
                                    territories under its domination to self-determination and
                                    independence;

Immediate cessation of all acts of repression and withdrawal
                                    of all the military and other forces at present employed for the
                                    purpose;

Promulgation of an unconditional political amnesty and
                                    establishment of conditions which will permit the free
                                    functioning of political parties;
